Package de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DateParseException  
    DuplicateKeyException
    This exception is thrown, when a record shall be inserted with an id, which already exists in the datastore
    InsertException
    An InsertException is thrown, when during insert of a record into the gateway an error occured
    MappingException
    An exception which is thrown during the mapping process
    NoSuchMapperException  
    NoSuchRecordException
    Exception is thrown, when an expected record wasn't found
    QueryException
    An exception which occured during a query execution
    QueryParameterException  
    TypeHandlerException
    Exception is thrown when an error in the use of ITypeHandler was detected
    UnsupportedKeyGenerator
    This exception is thrown, if an IKeyGenerator was requested by from an IDataStore which is not supported
    WriteException
    An WriteException is thrown, when during writing a record into the gateway an error occured
